name: Sound Experiments 001 - Babby's First Track
description:
I've decided that in order to produce the piece I have in my mind's eye, I need to first practice and develop some new skills. So in this project I will be sharing some of my experimentation on Pico-8 sounds, music or otherwise. 

In this case, I'm accompanying the track with some noise visuals, including a new technique I hope to explore more in the future.

:)
